# TaskPulse — Full-Stack React + Python + SQL Rebuild with World-Class Animations

Convert the existing 8 static HTML pages of TaskPulse (an enterprise project management SaaS) into a production-grade full-stack application with animations that rival Apple/FAANG quality.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **This is a massive project.** We are building a complete full-stack app with 8+ pages, a Python API, SQL database, JWT auth, and cinema-grade animations using Framer Motion + Three.js. This plan is structured in phases so we can build incrementally and validate as we go.

> [!WARNING]
> **Database Choice**: I'll use **SQLite** for local development (zero setup). If you want PostgreSQL or MySQL for production, let me know and I'll adjust.

> [!WARNING]
> **Three.js Scope**: Three.js will be used strategically (landing page hero 3D scene, login page ambient orb, page transition effects) — NOT on every page, to keep performance smooth. Overusing 3D degrades UX. Let me know if you want more or less 3D.

## Open Questions

1. **Authentication**: Should users actually be able to register/login, or is this a demo with mock data? *(I'll build real JWT auth either way)*
2. **Deployment**: Do you want Docker setup or just local dev for now?
3. **Any additional pages** beyond the 8 we have? (Landing, Login, Sign Up, Dashboard, Projects, Kanban, Task Detail, Settings)

---

## Architecture Overview

```
taskpulse/
├── frontend/                    # React + Vite + TailwindCSS v4
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/          # Reusable UI components
│   │   │   ├── layout/          # Sidebar, TopBar, Footer
│   │   │   ├── ui/              # GlassCard, Button, Input, Badge, etc.
│   │   │   └── three/           # Three.js scenes (Hero, Orb, Particles)
│   │   ├── pages/               # 8 page components
│   │   ├── hooks/               # Custom hooks (useAuth, useAPI, etc.)
│   │   ├── context/             # Auth context, Theme context
│   │   ├── lib/                 # API client, utils
│   │   ├── styles/              # Global CSS + design tokens
│   │   └── assets/              # Static assets
│   └── package.json
│
├── backend/                     # Python FastAPI
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── main.py              # FastAPI app entry
│   │   ├── models.py            # SQLAlchemy ORM models
│   │   ├── schemas.py           # Pydantic schemas
│   │   ├── database.py          # SQLite connection + session
│   │   ├── auth.py              # JWT auth utilities
│   │   ├── routes/              # API route modules
│   │   │   ├── auth.py          # Login, Register, Token refresh
│   │   │   ├── projects.py      # CRUD for projects
│   │   │   ├── tasks.py         # CRUD for tasks
│   │   │   ├── users.py         # Profile, settings
│   │   │   └── dashboard.py     # Aggregated stats
│   │   └── seed.py              # Seed database with demo data
│   └── requirements.txt
│
└── taskpulse.db                 # SQLite database file
```

