## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Backend (Python + FastAPI + SQLite)

#### [NEW] `backend/requirements.txt`
- FastAPI, uvicorn, SQLAlchemy, pydantic, python-jose (JWT), passlib, bcrypt

#### [NEW] `backend/app/database.py`
- SQLite connection via SQLAlchemy
- Session dependency for FastAPI

#### [NEW] `backend/app/models.py`
- **User**: id, name, email, password_hash, bio, avatar_url, role, created_at
- **Project**: id, name, description, icon, status (active/planning/staging), progress, due_date, owner_id
- **Task**: id, title, description, project_id, assignee_id, status (todo/in_progress/done), priority (high/medium/low), due_date, tags, checklist (JSON), created_at
- **Comment**: id, task_id, user_id, content, created_at
- **UserSettings**: id, user_id, theme, email_digest, push_alerts, team_activity

#### [NEW] `backend/app/schemas.py`
- Pydantic request/response models for all entities

#### [NEW] `backend/app/auth.py`
- JWT token creation/validation, password hashing with bcrypt

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routes/auth.py`
- `POST /api/auth/register` — Create account
- `POST /api/auth/login` — Returns JWT token
- `GET /api/auth/me` — Get current user from token

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routes/projects.py`
- `GET /api/projects` — List all projects with progress
- `POST /api/projects` — Create project
- `GET /api/projects/:id` — Single project with tasks
- `PUT /api/projects/:id` — Update project

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routes/tasks.py`
- `GET /api/tasks?project_id=X` — Tasks filtered by project
- `POST /api/tasks` — Create task
- `PUT /api/tasks/:id` — Update task (status, priority, assignee)
- `GET /api/tasks/:id` — Task detail with comments & checklist
- `POST /api/tasks/:id/comments` — Add comment

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routes/dashboard.py`
- `GET /api/dashboard/stats` — Active projects count, total tasks, team pulse score
- `GET /api/dashboard/activity` — Recent team activity feed
- `GET /api/dashboard/velocity` — Chart data for project velocity
- `GET /api/dashboard/overdue` — Overdue tasks

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routes/users.py`
- `PUT /api/users/profile` — Update name, bio, avatar
- `GET /api/users/settings` — Get notification preferences
- `PUT /api/users/settings` — Update notification preferences

#### [NEW] `backend/app/seed.py`
- Populate database with realistic demo data matching the HTML mockups (Acme Corp, Aether Engine project, team members, kanban tasks, etc.)

#### [NEW] `backend/app/main.py`
- FastAPI app with CORS middleware, route registration, startup seeding

