## Tech Stack Summary

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend Framework** | React 18 + Vite |
| **Styling** | TailwindCSS v4 |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion 11 |
| **3D Graphics** | Three.js via @react-three/fiber |
| **Drag & Drop** | @hello-pangea/dnd |
| **Charts** | Recharts |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 |
| **Backend** | Python FastAPI |
| **ORM** | SQLAlchemy |
| **Database** | SQLite |
| **Auth** | JWT (python-jose) + bcrypt |
| **API Client** | Axios |

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. **Backend**: Start FastAPI server, hit all API endpoints with curl/httpx
2. **Frontend**: `npm run dev` — verify all pages render, navigation works
3. **Auth flow**: Register → Login → Access protected routes → Logout
4. **Data flow**: Create project → Add tasks → View on kanban → Update status

### Manual Verification
1. **Browser testing**: Open in browser, check all 8 pages visually
2. **Animation quality**: Verify smooth 60fps transitions, no jank
3. **Three.js performance**: Confirm hero scene runs smoothly
4. **Responsive**: Check mobile/tablet breakpoints
5. **Dark theme consistency**: Verify all pages match the obsidian design system
